public class JsonParser
extends BaseParser

An implementation of Parser designed to fetch JSON encoded data, as per RFC4627.

Method Detail

parse

public List<JsonItem> parse()
Parses all items available at this parser's URL. Top level items will be stored in the returned list.

Note: It may be necessary for some web services to parse the top level item as a JsonItem and further items as JsonItems from it.

Returns:
a List containing JSON items fetched from this parser's URL.
